### 3. Lib Layer

#### [NEW] `lib/db.ts` — Prisma singleton

Standard Next.js Prisma singleton pattern using `globalThis`.

#### [NEW] `lib/crypto.ts` — AES-256 encryption

- `encryptKey(plaintext: string): string` — encrypts with AES-256-GCM using `AI_KEY_SECRET` env var
- `decryptKey(ciphertext: string): string` — decrypts
- Format: `iv:authTag:encrypted` (base64-encoded segments)
- Fails fast if `AI_KEY_SECRET` is missing or not 32 characters

#### [NEW] `lib/ai.ts` — Vercel AI SDK provider routing

- `getAIModel(userId: string): Promise<LanguageModel>` — fetches active AIKey, decrypts, returns the correct provider model
- Maps `AIProvider` enum → SDK provider factory (`@ai-sdk/anthropic`, `@ai-sdk/openai`, etc.)

#### [NEW] `lib/redis.ts` — Upstash Redis client (stub)

- Exports an `undefined`-safe Redis client — logs a warning if env vars are missing but doesn't crash

#### [NEW] `lib/resend.ts` — Resend client (stub)

- Exports a Resend client instance — logs a warning if `RESEND_API_KEY` is missing

