### 8. AI Task Assignment Engine

#### [NEW] `app/api/ai/assign-tasks/route.ts` — POST

- Fetches ProjectBrief + GroupMembers + User profiles
- Fetches active AIKey for session user
- Constructs structured prompt with: idea, solution, deadline, scope, each member's name + skills + level
- Calls AI via Vercel AI SDK with `generateText` or `generateObject`
- Expects JSON: `[{ userId, role, tasks: [{ title, description, estimatedDays }] }]`
- Saves roles to GroupMember, tasks to Task table
- Updates ProjectBrief status to ANALYSED
- Includes JSON retry logic (retry once if malformed)

